name: DPW Holdings
short_description: DPW Holdings, Inc. designs, develops, manufactures, and sells power system solutions for the military/aerospace, medical, and industrial-telecommunication industries in North America and Europe.
long_description: DPW Holdings, Inc. designs, develops, manufactures, and sells power system solutions for the military/aerospace, medical, and industrial-telecommunication industries in North America and Europe. The company offers custom power system solutions; high-grade flexibility series power supply products, such as power rectifiers; and value-added services for original equipment manufacturers. It also provides power conversion and distribution equipment, direct current/active current inverters, and uninterrupted power supply products; and radio frequency and microwave filters, diplexers, multiplexers, detectors, switch filters, integrated assemblies, and detector logarithmic video amplifiers, as well as provides commercial loans. In addition, the company distributes value added power supply solutions, UPS systems, fans, filters, line cords, and other power-related components; manufactures specialized electronic systems for the military market; and owns and operates the Prep Kitchen brand restaurants located in the San Diego area. DPW Holdings, Inc. sells its products directly through its sales force, as well as through independent manufacturer representatives and distributors. The company was formerly known as Digital Power Corporation and changed its name to DPW Holdings, Inc. in December 2017. DPW Holdings, Inc. was founded in 1969 and is based in Newport Beach, California.
